r the loan approval you will receive the money in your bank account in no more than 10 - 15 days</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20tab%20%2D%2D%3E--><div class="tab-pane fade" id="tab-3" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-3"><div class="boxmlthemeone55 textmlthemeone55"><span class="editmlthemeone55">edit</span> <span class="savemlthemeone55">save</span><p>Our commissions are the lowest in the market and you can rest assured we're doing our best to keep it that way.</p><p>Besides low commissions and transfer fees here are the reasons you should choose Cedo as your loan provider:</p><ul class="v-space-lg"><li>Impartiality and objectiveness regarding social status</li><li>Kind staff including sympathetic credit counselors</li><li>Low interest rates according to regulated legislation</li></ul></div></div><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20tab%20%2D%2D%3E--></div><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20nav%20tabs%20content%20%2D%2D%3E--></div><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20col%20%2D%2D%3E--><div class="col-lg-6"><div class="boxmlthemeone23"><span class="editmlthemeone23">edit</span> <span class="savemlthemeone23">save</span> <input type="file" id="imageUploadmlthemeone23" accept=".png, .jpg, .jpeg" data-cke-editable="1" contenteditable="false"> <label class="imageUploadmlthemeone23" for="imageUploadmlthemeone23">&nbsp;</label> <img id="imagePreviewmlthemeone23" class="description-image" data-cke-saved-src=" //via.placeholder.com/500x430/98bf5d/fff" src=" //via.placeholder.com/500x430/98bf5d/fff" alt="description"></div></div><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20col%20%2D%2D%3E--></div><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20row%20%2D%2D%3E--></div><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20container%20%2D%2D%3E--></div><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20pills%20%2D%2D%3E--><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20description%202%20%2D%2D%3E--></section><d